creator: Vemate
descriptionHtml:
About Vemate

VEVE collectibles data analysis and updates
The Phase 1 application will offer Floor price updates faster than any other analysis application on the Market, it will put various tools at the disposal of our users, free of charge.

During Phase 2, the application will morph to become a Learning, Information, Trading Analysis, Minting and Marketplace for NFTs, aiming to challenge the monopoly of OpenSea and lowering the market entrance threshold. Thus enabling the remaining 90% of the Crypto market to become involved with the NFT market. Moreover, Vemate is planning to change the structural layout of NFT trading to a configuration which would allow fast paced volume trading thus opening the door for retail investors.

Pre-alpha functionalities - Functions of the app are limited in scope and depth at the moment and there may be bugs encountered throughout the various screens of the app. Furthermore, the structural layout of the application may be subject to change as the tools are improved and implemented.

Appearance - Being in a pre-alpha stage, the appearance of the application is below the standards of the finished and polished product.

Floor prices are updated at approximately 54 minute intervals at the moment with this number expected to be decreased to approximately 15 minutes within the next 2 weeks.

Vault Value is only partially functional at the moment with an update expected in the next 2 weeks which will enable several of the functions planned for the application.

Tiered System - This will be implemented upon completion of the First stage of Phase 1
Free access Tier: The basic app which will provide floor price updates every 40 minutes as well as Vault Value information will be completely free to use.
Freemium Tier 1: The basic app will provide floor price updates every 15 minutes, Vault Value information and access to our surprise tool which will improve reaction times, among several other useful tools. Users who want to access these freemium features of the app will be required to hold the equivalent of $100 in Vemate tokens in their wallets.

There are a number of features in the planning stages which will further expand the offerings of the Phase 1 application. Therefore, the Vemate development team welcomes all constructive feedback, which we plan to use in order to improve and expand the scope of the application.
descriptionShort: Vemate - A Digital Collector's Best Friend

title: Vemate

creator: Vemate
descriptionHtml:
VEVE collectibles data analysis and updates, on your phone!

⁃ Price & mint alarms
⁃ Sorting by low mints
⁃ Floor price updates via VeVe API
⁃ Rarity filters
⁃ Сhart perspective
⁃ Personal Vault & Wishlist
- Automatic collection imports
⁃ Collection value analysis
⁃ With much more to come

Vemate has signed an API agreement VeVe and struck a community partnership with ECOMI, VeVe’s parent company. However, Vemate is solely responsible for the app.

There are a number of features in the planning stages that will further expand the offerings of the app. Therefore, the Vemate development team welcomes all constructive feedback, which we plan to use in order to improve and expand the scope of the application.
